14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
16 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
17 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma
18 Advanced Manufacturing Incentive Act of 2025".
19 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
20 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
21 The Oklahoma Advanced Manufacturing Incentive Act of 2025 shall
22 establish a tax incentive and direct grant program to attract
23 manufacturers of low-grade waste heat electrification technology to
24
